## Issue Description

{{entity.refs.linear.description}}

## How to Implement

1. Read the codebase at {{entity.artifacts.codebasePath}} to understand the relevant code.
2. Read CLAUDE.md in the repo root for project-specific gotchas.
3. Implement the fix. Keep changes minimal — this is a hotfix, not a refactor.
4. Write or update tests to cover the fix.
5. Run the CI gate: `pnpm lint && pnpm format && pnpm build`
6. Run targeted tests: `npx vitest run <test-file>` — NEVER `pnpm test` in worktrees.
7. Push and create a PR with `gh pr create`.

## Signal

Say `PR created: <the full GitHub PR URL>` when done.

